e consilia the keepers of creative thaumaturgies created and weilded by the mages of the city and the keepers of that knowledge.%0a> %0a161,164c149,150%0a%3c They are the law keepers and prosecutors and defenders of those accused of breaking the laws.%0a%3c %0a%3c *'''Factotums Need Academics 3 and be completely familiar with the laws of the consilia'''%0a%3c %0a---%0a> '''Factotums Need Academics 3 and be completely familiar with the laws of the consilia'''. They are the law keepers and prosecutors and defenders of those accused of breaking the laws.%0a> %0a175,177c161%0a%3c Masked executors of justice who carry out the sentences the Consilium passes. Only a Guardian of the Veil can hold this post, and most Interfectors serve all the Consilia within the local Guardian Caucus.  Interfectors are the Right hand of the Consilium when punishment is to be meted out it is the Interfector who performs it. Be it Soul Scourging or The Like it is their solemn duty to uphold the laws edicts and judgement of the consilia.  %0a%3c %0a%3c *'''Sentinel Deputy must have applicable combat and investigation or infiltration skills.  Interfector must be active GoV and completed one mission at GoV behest.'''%0a---%0a> Masked executors of justice who carry out the sentences the Consilium passes. Only a Guardian of the Veil can hold this post, and most Interfectors serve all the Consilia within the local Guardian Caucus.  Interfectors are the Right hand of the Consilium when punishment is to be meted out it is the Interfector who performs it. Be it Soul Scourging or The Like it is their solemn duty to uphold the laws edicts and judgement of the consilia.  '''Sentinel Deputy must have applicable combat and investigation or infiltration skills.  Interfector must be active GoV and completed one mission at GoV behest.'''%0a
